HEADWORD: Hearthstone
<hw>Hearth"stone`</hw> <pr>(-st⟦omac⟧n`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Stone
forming the hearth; hence, the fireside; home.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Chords of memory, stretching from every battlefield and patriot
